<h1 style="color: #e8e8e8; font-size: 40px; margin-top: 5%;">Join the story!</h1>
<div class="main" id="com-story">
  
  <ul class="cards">
    <li class="cards_item">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card_image"><img src="https://image.freepik.com/free-vector/curved-pumpkins-ghosts-halloween-background_52683-23347.jpg"></div>
        <div class="card_content">
          <h2 class="card_title">Time for some horror!</h2>
          <p class="card_text">If you are looking for some bone chilling content to read and write with, you are in the right place! Continue and make others shiver, literally.</p>
          <a href="/horror" ><button class="btn card_btn" style="margin-top: 5%">Take me!</button></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="cards_item">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card_image"><img src="https://image.freepik.com/free-vector/writing-letter-article-writer-author-workplace-desk-table-illustration_101884-1036.jpg"></div>
        <div class="card_content">
          <h2 class="card_title">Poets Think Alike</h2>
          <p class="card_text">But exactly how alike? Come explore beautiful poetry with us and join the poetry flow.</p>
          <a href="/poetry"><button class="btn card_btn">Take me!</button></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>


    <li class="cards_item">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card_image"><img src="https://image.freepik.com/free-photo/couple-holding-heart-balloon-valentine-s-day-illustration_53876-98020.jpg"></div>
        <div class="card_content">
          <h2 class="card_title">Feel the love vibes?</h2>
          <p class="card_text">Missing your special one or thinking about making them immortal through words? Then, do not look any further. Just hop in here and join the lovebirds!</p>
          <a href="/romance"><button class="btn card_btn" style="margin-top: 8%">Take me!</button></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>

   

  </ul>
